        <p>
            <b>Used plugins</b>: <a href="server-routing.md">Routing</a>,
            <a href="https://kotlinlang.org/api/kotlinx.serialization/">kotlinx.serialization</a>,
            <a href="server-serialization.md">Content Negotiation</a>,
